  "text": "The logarithm of the ratios for all valid spots on each array was normalized by locally weighted linear regression (LOWESS). Descriptions of Microarray Data Preprocessing can be found in our previous studies [CITATION_1] . The normalized log ratios were then processed gene-by-gene using a log linear model [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . This model describes the normalized log ratio as follows:",
